<title>Send Account Overrides</title>

<p>If you use more than one email account, you can define which account should always be used as your sender address:</p>
<list>
<item><p>When replying to mail in specific <link xref="mail-folders">folders</link>.</p></item>
<item><p>When replying to certain email addresses, names, or parts of email addresses or names.</p></item>
</list>
<p>These settings are available under <guiseq><gui>Edit</gui><gui>Preferences</gui><gui>Composer Preferences</gui><gui>Send Account</gui></guiseq>.</p>

